<br>
Item haste does stack with spell/song haste.<br>
<br>
In most cases, the haste from a song and spell do not stack (but the other buffs do). There are a few haste songs that do stack with spells (the new Luclin ones).<br>
<br>
The highest haste from your items is the one used. The highest haste from spell/song is the one used.<br>
